column33:
* Manual preparation instead of blasting was more effective.
* 2 days discussing whether we'll perform the machining in house.
* Rework on Diverter Base due to pre machining failure. Impact of 2 weeks on the chronogram;

* Sheaves with severe corrosion, taking longer than usual to prepare for dimensional inspection;
* Prioritization of shotblasting/painting of DDM 1000 project, 5 days delay;
* Not necessary NDT inspections.

* 1 week quotation delay;
* Issues found on Cylinder chromium process. Will be necessary welding and machining process (W32);
* Second rework on hydraulic portic #1
* Spare parts will be sent by the costumer.
